    "The representation phase entails extracting features that describe the quality of the writing.",
    "To achieve this, AES utilizes methods from NLP and machine learning to extract these features.",
    "The second phase extends from the chosen essay quality features and transforms the representation into a numerical score, assumed to reflect the quality level of the essays.",
    "In this section, we will delve into the essay representation methods utilized in the papers included in this survey.",
    "Handcrafted feature engineering refers to the manual process of extracting features that are associated with characteristics of words, phrases, sentences, paragraphs and the entire essay."
